                  <span class="auction-chip">電話は1社のみ</span>
                  <span class="auction-chip">手数料無料</span>
                  <span class="auction-chip">アプリで進捗通知</span>
                </div>

                <div class="download-panel">
                  <h3 class="download-title">DL率25%へ向けた訴求</h3>
                  <div class="download-meter"><span></span></div>
                  <p class="download-caption">不安を先に消し、AI査定の体験価値を押し出す</p>
                  <div class="button-row">
                    <button class="primary-button pink-button" type="button" id="compareButton">訴求を確認</button>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="floating-score">
                  <span>CVR目標</span>
                  <strong>25%</strong>
                </div>

                <div class="swipe-hint">
